g.text: Ticketmaster is an online platform that allows users to purchase tickets for concerts, sporting events, theater, and other live entertainment.
1. Users should be able to view events
2. Users should be able to search for events
3. Users should be able to book tickets to events
1. System should favor consistency >> availability for booking. Availability >> consistency for search.
2. System should scale to handle bursty traffic (eg. Popular event) 100x normal traffic load
